    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_45205">That means the weapon's base damage is 1-6.  In 1d6 the 1 means you roll 1 and the d6 means the die has 6 sides on it.<br />
<br />
So substitute 1-6 in for the dagger's 1-4 in the above example to see how damage is calculated.<br />
 </div>
